casebody.data:
No. 1159. Gutiérrez et al., Plaintiffs and Appellants, v. Foix et al., Defendants and Respondents. Decided June 2, 1914. Mr. Antonio J. Amadeo for the appellants. Mr. Francisco Gonzales for the respondents.

Motion sustained.

Appeal from the District Court of Humacao in a case of intervention in ownership of real property. Motion by the appellants for leave to withdraw the appeal.
